{
  "stem": "8962.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Shortly after we left, the people who now lived in the house, threw them out of the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was a Jewish community in Cologne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were very close to Cologne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the Jewish community in Cologne took them into a home where they were living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there, they were really better off than in Bedburg, where they were living, because they had back up support.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there were some people who took care of them, not realizing that one day, everybody got picked up out of that home and got shipped to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in America already, by then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we wrote them, and there was no answer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we wrote them again, and there was no answer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Until finally, we got a letter saying that they were-- very short letter-- in Cologne, in this old age home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Jewish community in Cologne notified us that they were picked up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That everybody, all the old people in that home, were picked up, put into a cattle car.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my cousins, who had fled to Argentina, got the notice because they inquired.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Germans-- they kept such damn good records-- said that they went into the cattle car, but they never got out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they opened the car in Theresienstadt, they must have been dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At least they didn't have to go into the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if that's a consolation or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left-- we got into Holland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were on the train in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The lights were out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the train stopped, and that was the border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, mom, I only have $2.30 left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm going to give it to a charity box.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
